{
  "stem": "15732.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "From the Jewish population that we had in Czernowitz, I think that 30,000 eventually survived.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think there were 120,000 or 100,000.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But a third survived, which is comparative to Poland.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A-- a very good percentage still.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Germans pressed on the Romanians to start with the extermination of the Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They tried to find a [? modus ?] how to do it and still not to do it the German way-- how, as Germany had called it, extermination camps.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I do not know their mentality, why and what.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I just know that after several deportations, they stopped.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Romanians stopped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was rumored in the ghetto that they got a very high amount of money in Bucharest, which is the capital city of Romania-- they got a high amount of money as a bribe, in order to stop the annihilation.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I do not know as much as that is truth or not or if it was only rumor.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think after two or three months.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was winter that-- we are talking about 1941.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In spring 1942, the thing starts again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were still--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When the second wave-- we called it the wave-- the second wave of deportation started, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we were very fearful, certainly.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father first bought himself a certificate that he's not-- because he has a heart condition-- that he is not transportable, that he cannot go on a transport, which was, for the money that it costs, it was really not very much.",
      "word_count": 43
    }
  ],
